绍兴医患互敬照片被疑摆拍，院方回应：没有强制3岁男孩鞠躬。
Shaoxing doctor and patient mutual respect photos are suspected of swinging, hospital response: no compulsory 3-year-old boys bow.
刘世龙。
Liu Shilong.
界面新闻                      。
Interface news.
界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：@新华视点实习记者：刘世龙“ 该幅照片因与20世纪初时杭州广济医院（现浙江大学医学院附属第二医院）院长梅藤根与小患者相互鞠躬的一张照片颇为相似，而受到网友热议，也被称为“跨越百年”的医患互敬照片。
2007-9-25 21: 48 "This photo is similar to that of a patient bowing to each other at Hangzhou Guangji Hospital in the early 20th century (now the Second Hospital attached to Zhejiang University Medical School) and a photo of doctors and patients bowing to each other.
”2020年2月23日，新华社旗下@新华视点发布一张3岁男孩与医护人员互相鞠躬的图片引起外界关注。
A picture of three-year-old boys bowing to medical staff at Xinhua @ Xinhua News Agency on February 23, 2020 drew attention.
@新华视点消息称，2月22日，浙江省绍兴市中心医院隔离病房一位3岁的小患者治愈出院，向护士阿姨鞠躬致敬，护士也顺势对其回礼鞠躬，这一幕恰巧被拍了下来。
A 3-year-old patient in the isolation ward of Shaoxing City Central Hospital in Zhejiang Province was hospitalized on Feb. 22 and bowed to his aunt and nurse, according to Xinhua News Agency.
据悉，该小患者有发热症状，核酸检测为阴性，经治愈后出院。
It is reported that this small patient has febrile symptoms, nucleic acid test is negative, be cured after discharge.
该幅照片因与20世纪初时杭州广济医院（现浙江大学医学院附属第二医院）院长梅藤根与小患者相互鞠躬的一张照片颇为相似，而受到网友热议，也被称为“跨越百年”的医患互敬照片。
The photo, which resembles a picture of patients bowing to each other at Hangzhou Guangji Hospital (now the No. 2 Hospital attached to Zhejiang University School of Medicine) in the early 20th century, has been hotly debated among netizens, also known as the "100-year-old" photo of doctors and patients.
另据绍兴越牛新闻客户端报道，当天出院时，小男孩好几次对精心照顾他的“护士妈妈”表达了感谢。
According to Shaoxing Yue Niu News client reported that the same day when discharged from the hospital, the little boy several times to take care of his "nurse mother" expressed gratitude.
分别前，泽泽突然对护士鞠了一躬，护士也被孩子的可爱和真诚感动，随即也弯下腰来，鞠躬答谢。
Before parting, Zezer suddenly bowed to the nurse, who was also moved by the child's sweetness and sincerity, and then bowed down to acknowledge it.
而这感人的一幕刚好被路过的同事记录了下来。
The touching scene was just recorded by a passing colleague.
不过，界面新闻注意到，也有网友针对绍兴市中心医院这张照片发出不同声音，认为有摆拍嫌疑。
However, the interface news noted that there are also netizens Shaoxing City Central Hospital this photo issued different voices, that there are suspicion of posing.
“新闻图片讲的是时间的真实性，一个三岁孩子真的有这样高的文化和人生感悟境界吗？”有网友对此质疑。
"News pictures tell the truth of the time, a three-year-old really have such a high level of culture and life perception?" Some netizens questioned.
@新华视点称上述照片由浙江省绍兴市中心医院提供。
@ Xinhua said the photos were provided by the Shaoxing Central Hospital in Zhejiang Province.
2月24日上午，绍兴市中心医院对界面新闻回应称，该照片是偶然所得，并没有摄影师或其他成年人指使小男孩鞠躬。
On the morning of Feb. 24, Shaoxing Central Hospital told the Interface News that the photo had been taken by accident and no photographers or other adults had ordered the boy to bow.
据该医院办公室工作人员介绍，男孩出院当天，医院举办了一个欢送仪式。
The hospital held a farewell ceremony the day the boy was discharged from the hospital, the hospital said.
小男孩在等父母来接时，负责照顾他的护士一直在陪其玩耍。
The nurse who had taken care of the boy was playing with his parents while they were waiting for him to come.
因为欢送仪式需要照片，现场有人负责拍照，所以在小男孩做出鞠躬这一突然举动时，就被恰好拍了下来，“当时只有他的爷爷奶奶陪护，所以并不像网友怀疑的那样，不存在被父母强制要求的可能。
"He was accompanied by his grandparents, so there was no possibility of being forced by his parents, as some netizens suspected," he said
”院方没有透露当事小男孩及其家人的具体情况。
The hospital did not disclose the circumstances of the boy and his family.
“本来我们只是在自己医生朋友圈里面传了一下，可能被媒体记者关注到了，图片就被要走了，没想到在网络上火了。
"We were just in their own circle of doctors and friends, may be concerned by the media reporters, the picture was to be left, did not expect in the network on the fire.
”该医院办公室工作人员表示。
"The hospital office staff said.
